{
  "stem": "1387.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's about 3 kilometers, 3 1/2 kilometers near Zloczow-- between Zloczow and Sasow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were the killing grounds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And around 11 o'clock that morning, I found the clothes of my brother-in-law, my mother, my sister, my brother, and their five-year-old child.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Clothing-- I found them while I was selecting and working in that, in that position.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How do I know exactly that it were their clothes?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was wearing the jacket of a suit, and my brother-in-law was wearing the slacks from the same suit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I recognized it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I took it out separately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in it, I found documentation of my family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I found a $20 gold piece sewn in in his belt, belt area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as I was selecting those clothes and found many valuables-- many diamonds and money and everything that was brought out and was separated to give to the Germans, that $20 piece, I kept.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I know for a fact that my family [NON-ENGLISH] was 26 days in the month of Adar, on 1942.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] I also recall vividly that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the next morning I walked out into the streets of Zloczow to see what's going on because we could hear a lot of shooting and a lot of noises.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not that far away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw the rabbi's wife, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] their daughter, their son [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] on a open truck, being transferred, obviously, to [NON-ENGLISH], to the killing grounds.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] wife.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was screaming to me, [NON-ENGLISH], tell the world what you just saw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tell the world what's going on here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was an experience I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
